{"tid":364741,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch] Splatoon2 [17] 第一頁Q&A 睇咗先問","createTime":"2017-08-18T15:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T15:52:32.000Z","uid":5480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1610d4f05d298690714a1ba55e08ddeed506c1ed","tid":364741,"uid":5480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_splatoon2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_splatoon2.png&h=19230c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Splatoon<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>  (スプラトゥーン<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>)</strong></span><br />\n遊戲/Amiibo/JoyCon/ProController 發售日期：2017-7-21<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg&h=c9c49d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg&h=dea22259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSplatoon是一款4對4 第三人稱射擊遊戲，與其他射擊遊戲有所不同<br />\n玩家需利用武器把地面塗色，佔色面積較多的一方獲勝 <br />\n<br />\n官方介紹片段(中文):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCROuiq-YjlI&d=On4r%2BQyPtzvYDtOv2KsQZ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8ac5674d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI</a><br />\n<br />\n日本官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fswitch%2Faab6a&d=On4r%2BQyPtzvYDtOv2KsQZ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d35c4273\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a</a><br />\n<br />\n日本官方Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/splatoonjp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsplatoonjp&d=On4r%2BQyPtzvYDtOv2KsQZ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bac5bc2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/splatoonjp</a><br />\n<br />\n香港官方網站/ 遊戲介紹:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/splatoon2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsplatoon2&d=On4r%2BQyPtzvYDtOv2KsQZ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0c66b9d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/splatoon2</a><br />\n<br />\n歐美官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"http://splatoon.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsplatoon.nintendo.com&d=On4r%2BQyPtzvYDtOv2KsQZ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f1954e53\" target=\"_blank\">http://splatoon.nintendo.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>現時會出現的場地 </strong></span></span><br />\n(8揀2, 每2小時轉一次)<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFFhzlVUAAAXCEg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFFhzlVUAAAXCEg.jpg&h=72a98bf9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n開Post用文件<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc%2F&d=On4r%2BQyPtzvYDtOv2KsQZ%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3aa06050\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc/</a>"}]}